	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>That is not the only way to do DKP.&nbsp;&nbsp;Guilds such as mine (NoV, top guild on Fennin Ro) do DKP on a pure buy sell system, person with the highest DKP and over 20% raid attendence (30 Day) wins the item.  <br><br>The problem with some DKP is where the items don't take as many points out of the system as they put in.  Think of this formula:<br><br>(Mob DKP * Players in Raid) = (Value of all drops)<br><br>If this formula is not kept balenced then the new members are at a severe disadvantage because the active people with always have more points. <br><br>Reikes<br>65 Rogue<br>NoV<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
